-------------------VMware Certified Associate-------------------
>>Partir résau de la virtualisation: when creating a vm we need to plug it in a network 
            >On utilise le vSwitch pour assurer les échanges réseaux entre les VMs
             au niveua de chaque hyperviseur.
>>VM files & live state:
    -Datastore: is simply any storage technology that has been prepared to house VM files
>>vCenter :-used to manage our vsphere environement 
           -used to manage many ESXI hosts at once
  >Some features of vCenter : VMotion,DRS,FT,HA,DRS storage,storage vMotion...
  >vCenter Appliance : est une VM préconfigurée et optimisée pour l'éxecution du  vCenter.
  >Def of each feature : 
      --vMotion: used to reduce the downtime
      --HA :provides host failover protection
      --migrate VMs from host to host ,or site to site 
      --Fault Tolerance: runs an identical copy of the vm on another host  
  >Shared Storage: is a system storage that is accessible to all esxi hosts 
 
